  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nCommunitySettingsView is needlessly loaded for every loaded community even if the user doesn't have the rights to open the settings view, or doesn't need this view in the current session.\r\n\r\nOne proposal is to load the CommunitySettingsView on demand, when the user needs it, and to keep it loaded to preserve the state.",
